          <title>Harden erupts for 55, Clippers rout Hornets 131-116 in Paul's likely last game in North Carolina</title>
          <description><![CDATA[James Harden made 10 3-pointers and scored a franchise-record 55 points, and the Los Angeles Clippers beat the Charlotte Hornets 131-116 hours after 12-time All-Star point guard Chris Paul released a video on social media hinting at retirement after the season ends.]]></description>
